        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>Augt 23d 5612</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Rev &amp; Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">You will please to notice in the occident of<lb/> the next month
                that <persName>Mr. S.; Sedgwick</persName> Principal of the
                Methenal<add>?</add><lb/> &amp; Class: Institute has <sic>purched</sic> two lots of
                ground being <placeName>93 &amp; 95<lb/>
                    <sic>Sixt</sic> Av</placeName>: on which lots a building is in erecting of 100
                by 50 feet<lb/> a 5 Stories house, which building <sic>building</sic> when
                completed<lb/> will a splendid one and will <add>?</add> any School or College<lb/>
                in the <placeName>United States</placeName>, There will be <add>?</add> 1 a lecture
                Room<lb/> a debating Room for the discussion of Hebr Literature<lb/> 2 Gymnasiums,
                3d School Room, 4th languages &amp; 5th a Hebr<lb/> Department. The instructions
                will comprise</p>
            <p>Engl: Litar, Modrn Litar: Lat: &amp; Greek &amp; <add>?</add></p>
            <p>Drawing &amp; Arts of Design, Methen: &amp; Michan.</p>
            <p>Philosop &amp; Astron Chemis: &amp; Physic:</p>
            <p>Mor: intellet &amp; Ph<add>?</add> Phil</p>
            <p> Hebr <add>?</add>
                <add>?</add> Arab: &amp; <add>?</add> languages</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"> There will be engaged 8 Proff. Of the 1st class</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"> The whole will be a splendid affair, &amp; I</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"> hope when in town to visit it; it will be</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"> ready in the <date>15th of Sept</date>
                <add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">yours Truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <persName role="author">Simon C Nool</persName>
            </p>
            <p>N B we had the gratification last <date>Sabbath</date> that one of our<lb/> pupils of
                the school of my Congn gave <sic>prove</sic> of <add>קריאת התורה</add><lb/> the boy
                being only 11 years of age, is fully competent to act<lb/> as <add>בעל קורא</add> in
                my congn.</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philada</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Penn</placeName>
            </p>
